Paper: hep-th/9801039

Date: 1998-01-08

Title: Special Geometry and Compactification on a Circle

Authors: B. de Wit, B. Kleijn and S. Vandoren

Comments: 7pp, Latex, misprint corrected

Journal-ref: Fortsch.Phys. 47 (1999) 317-323

We discuss some consequences of our previous work on rigid special geometryin hypermultiplets in 4-dimensional Minkowski spacetime for supersymmetricgauge dynamics when one of the spatial dimensions is compactified on a circle.